<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>288</hymn_number>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
<lyrics>[V1]
 qióng yī diǎn wǒ men bù hòu huǐ, kǔ yī diǎn wǒ men bù hòu huǐ,
 tīng dào cháo mà shēng, wǒ men bù hòu huǐ, shòu dào duì fù wǒ men gèng bù hòu huǐ.
 tiān kōng dōu shì yī yàng de lán, shù yè dōu shì yī yàng de lǜ.
 wǒ men gēn suí zhǔ yě huì qiān rén xīn dòng, wǒ men zài shuō yī shēng yǒng yuǎn bù hòu huǐ.</lyrics>
<title>wǒ men bù hòu huǐ 迦南288</title>
</song>